VERSION 5.8 ;
DESIGN counter ;
UNITS DISTANCE MICRONS 1000 ;

NETS 2 ;
- clk ( clkbuf X ) ( ff0 CLK ) ( ff1 CLK )
  + ROUTED met1 ( 1000 2000 ) ( 1000 5000 )
    NEW met2 ( 1000 5000 ) M1M2_VIA ( 4000 5000 ) ;
- n0 ( u0 Y ) ( u1 A )
  + ROUTED met1 ( 2000 2000 ) ( 2000 2800 )
    NEW li1 ( 2000 2800 ) ( 2300 2800 ) ;
END NETS

END DESIGN
